      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Competitive. TASSORTING (6) resumes and a bold run is on the cards. Missed a whisker twice this track/trip before the spell and also placed here five starts back on debut. Brings a win and placing from the Sandown jumpouts and is sure to feature. IMMORTAL TRUTH (8) missed the placings first up but has since consolidated with two straight placings, the latest over 975m at Swan Hill. Should be right in it with the blinkers added. BIG KAPOW (1) returns to his home track after a fair run in town, beaten 3L at Caulfield Heath. He missed a whisker at Pakenham on debut and comes back to the shorter sprint. Should camp just off the leaders and also has claims. JACK THE JUDGE (4) and MAYNARD (5) head the rest, and they are in the mix.",
